<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣ - <span class="c2">(الْكَاتِب الْبَغْدَادِيّ)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
